        h2 What to Expect
        p Expect subversive and unconventional ideas that will challenge your thinking. Ideas less focused on implementations. A small event designed to promote constructive discussions between everyone involved. Expect a group of people who share an interest in securing the freedom of information and how we build systems around it.

